    "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nWhen we save the bookmark and then go to any other screen and come back to the reader screen the bookmark toggle is off and if we again click on the bookmark toggle to delete the saved bookmark it deletes the bookmark, if we again click on that toggle it again delete the bookmark which is already deleted, but it should save the bookmark at this time because it does not exist in the DB.\r\n\r\nThe same behavior is for saving the bookmark if we have not saved a bookmark and we go to any other screen and come back to the reader screen and then try to save the bookmark it saves that page as a bookmark, but if we again click on the toggle to remove the bookmark, it again saves the same bookmark into db but here it should remove the bookmark because it is already saved in the DB.\r\n\r\n**Steps to reproduce the behavior:**\r\n* Open any zim file\r\n* Click on the bookmark toggle to save the bookmark.\r\n* Go to the library screen and come back to the reader screen.\r\n* You will see the bookmark toggle is off but you saved the bookmark.\r\n* Then again click on the bookmark toggle it will show the bookmark deleted Then again click on the same button you will see the error.\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-android/assets/34593983/02d37269-6171-4503-a09f-fdad3d9afd3e\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-android/assets/34593983/96e195ad-2b03-47c6-9b71-5d774baadc27\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**Environment**\r\n- Version of Kiwix Android: 3.7.1\r\n- Device: Redmi Note 9\r\n- OS version : Android 12\r\n",
